abstract: Stihl Timbersports series, seeking publicity on its 30th anniversary, teams up with Adventures NYC to host lumberjack competition in Central Park.
lead_paragraph: Central Park hosted a daylong contest to determine the best lumberjack in the United States, at least for this year.

headline.main: Symphony of Chain Saws Cuts Clean Through Central Park’s Calm
